DeFi, DAOs, and NFTs are all part of a Fichtean struggle driving a dialectical evolution that gives birth to the end of history. I believe Hegelâ€™s vision is rational: he envisions a world where life became democratized, permissionless, transparent, and decentralized. Crypto.

With a new technological framework that enables reimplementation of an intelligently designed capitalistic system, how should we adopt the future? We turn to philosophy because crypto needs philosophy. Values need to be more than tokenizedâ€”they must be redefined and imposed.
